nearest integer.

@<Glob...@>=
@!two_to_the:array[0..30] of integer; {powers of two}
@!spec_log:array[1..28] of integer; {special logarithms}


@ @<Set init...@>=
two_to_the[0]:=1;
for k:=1 to 30 do two_to_the[k]:=2*two_to_the[k-1];
spec_log[1]:=93032640;
