|prim_size|, and it should be a prime number.

@<Compute the primitive code |h|@>=
h:=str_pool[j];
for k:=j+1 to j+l-1 do
  begin h:=h+h+str_pool[k];
  while h>=prim_prime do h:=h-prim_prime;
  end

